684
01:05:53,570 --> 01:05:55,370
Neboj sa. O chvíľu sa vrátime.

685
01:05:55,370 --> 01:05:56,940
Dobre.

686
01:05:59,310 --> 01:06:01,260
Kai Kai!

687
